high_descs: Turn left and head towards the sink on your right.
Pick up the left tomato from the sink.
Place the tomato on the top shelf of the fridge for it to cool and then take it back out.
Turn left towards the bin in between the fridge and sink.
Place the tomato in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool tomato in the bin.

high_descs: turn left and walk forwards until you're aligned with the kitchen sink on the right, then turn right and walk to the kitchen sink
grab the left tomato out of the sink there
turn right and walk over to the fridge on the left, turn left to face it
place the tomato inside of the fridge, let it cool and then take it back out
turn left and walk over to the garbage bin on the right
place the tomato inside of the garbage bin
anns.task_desc: place a cooled tomato inside of the garbage bin

high_descs: Turn left, walk across the room towards the white stove, hang a left and go to the silver sink at the end of the counter.
Pick up the tomato in the left corner of the sink behind the spoon.
Turn around to face the brown stool, turn left, walk towards the white door and turn left to face the fridge.
Put the tomato inside the fridge in the middle of the top shelf, close the door, let it chill for seven seconds, remove the tomato from inside and close the doors.
Turn left and walk to the tall gray container to the right in between the fridge and the counter.
Place the tomato inside the tall gray container near the back.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato in a tall container.
